OL,3,CWilliam, Kate and children join
OL,4,Ctraditional royal Easter service
OL,6,FThe Prince and Princess of Wales and
OL,7,Ftheir children have attended the
OL,8,Ftraditional Easter service for the
OL,9,Ffirst time since Kate's cancer
OL,10,Fdiagnosis.
OL,12,FKate and William were among senior
OL,13,Fmembers of the royal family to join
OL,14,Fthe King and Queen at the Easter
OL,15,FMatins service at St George's Chapel,
OL,16,FWindsor Castle on Sunday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
