OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775412669
OL,3,CWilliam, Kate and children join
OL,4,Ctraditional royal Easter service
OL,6,FWilliam waved to the large crowd
OL,7,Foutside the castle as the pair led a
OL,8,Fprocession to the service with their
OL,9,Fchildren, Prince George, Princess
OL,10,FCharlotte and Prince Louis.
OL,12,FCharlotte was in a tan coat and Kate
OL,13,Fwore an off-white ensemble of skirt,
OL,14,Fsmart jacket and leafy hat, while
OL,15,FWilliam and the boys wore dark blue
OL,16,Fsuits and ties.
OL,18,FCamilla arrived in red wool dress and
OL,19,Fcoat by Fiona Clare, a hat by Phillip
OL,20,FTreacy and a broach which belonged to
OL,21,Fthe late Queen Elizabeth II.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
