PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775412669
OL,3,CWilliam, Kate and children join
OL,4,Ctraditional royal Easter service
OL,6,FThe Waleses missed the service last
OL,7,Fyear as they were spending the weekend
OL,8,Fwith their children in Norfolk, and
OL,9,Fwere absent in 2024 as it came just
OL,10,Fover a week after Kate released an
OL,11,Femotional video message disclosing
OL,12,Fthat she had started a course of
OL,13,Fpreventative chemotherapy.
OL,15,FCharles and Camilla arrived by car in
OL,16,Ffront of the castle to a shout of "God
OL,17,Fsave the King" from the crowd on
OL,18,FSunday morning.
OL,26,@xD@cOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
