PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775412669
OL,3,CWilliam, Kate and children join
OL,4,Ctraditional royal Easter service
OL,6,FHe was later arrested in February on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,8,Foffice.
OL,10,FBeatrice and Eugenie, who are the
OL,11,FKing's nieces and have kept their
OL,12,Ftitles as princesses, joined the royal
OL,13,Ffamily for Christmas at Sandringham in
OL,14,FDecember.
OL,16,FIt is understood they will be at
OL,17,Ffamily celebrations in the future.
OL,19,FThe Princess Royal and Duke of
OL,20,FEdinburgh were also in attendance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
